          <source>istrstream Class</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="115" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The class describes an object that controls extraction of elements and encoded objects from a stream buffer of class <bpt id="p1">[</bpt>strstreambuf<ept id="p1">](../standard-library/strstreambuf-class.md)</ept>.</source>
        </trans-unit>
