        <trans-unit id="117" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The class describes an object that controls insertion of elements and encoded objects into a stream buffer of class <bpt id="p1">[</bpt>strstreambuf<ept id="p1">](../standard-library/strstreambuf-class.md)</ept>.</source>
